n: right;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);box-sizing: border-box;\">你也一定曾是某个人年少的欢喜&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);box-sizing: border-box;\">12.7&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);box-sizing: border-box;\">椰汁&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">赵雷《少年锦时》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我犹豫的白衬衫</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">青春口袋里面的第一只香烟</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">情窦初开的我，从不敢和你说</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">《不遇见》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我好怀念那张懵懂不经事的脸</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">骑白马衣翩翩，不知疲倦追赶着时间</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">田馥甄《小幸运》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我听见雨滴落在青青草地</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我听见远方下课钟声响起</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">可是我没有听见你的声音</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">认真呼唤我姓名</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">老狼《冬季校园》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那漂亮的女生，白发的先生</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">薛之谦《花儿和少年》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">还懵懂的花儿和少年</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">眉梢眼角带电，近情情怯</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">花儿长发披肩，少年似同学</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">纯净但也热烈。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">筷子兄弟《老男孩》</span></p></section><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">青春如同奔流的江河</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">一去不回来不及道别</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">《瓶中沙》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">树梢的枝丫，开满凤凰花</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">问你知道吗，成长需要代价</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">许巍《曾经的你》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">曾梦想仗剑走天涯</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">看一看世界的繁华</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">年少的心总有些轻狂</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">如今你四海为家</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">梁静茹《燕尾蝶》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">瓶中沙写的话，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 201, 101);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">问你是否还牵挂</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那张年轻熟悉的脸颊流长的发，逃离过的家</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">记得多年后的下午茶我们约好要一起喝下</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">既然不是毛毛虫就要壮烈的扑火，短暂青春要像烟火</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">老狼《同桌的你》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那时候天总是很蓝</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">日子总过得太慢</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">你总说毕业遥遥无期</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">转眼就各奔东西</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">张国荣《风再起时》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我回头再望，某年像失色</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">照片乍现，眼前这个茫然困惑少年</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">愿一生似歌投入每天永不变</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">许嵩《素颜》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">不画半熟的眼线，不用抹匀粉底液</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">暴雨天照逛街偷笑，别人花了脸</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">许嵩《如果当时》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">你和我曾经有共同爱好</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">谁的耳边总有绝句在萦绕</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我们俩用文言文对话真的很搞笑</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">还笑那曹操，贪恋着小乔</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">陈楚生《凤凰花又开》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">暖暖的海风轻轻的吹来，凤凰花又盛开</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我感到时间她过得真快，去年的花影还在</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">金玟岐《腻味》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那追着公车的少年，如今西装笔直挺面</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">许嵩《小烦恼没什么大不了》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">早晨六点不想起睡眠太少不长命</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">人类应该睡到自然醒</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">三天两头被考评成绩太低没自信谁在制造这么大压力</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">老狼《青春无悔》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">不忧愁的脸是我的少年不仓惶的眼，等岁月改变最熟悉你我的街，已是人去夕阳斜，人和人互相在街边道再见</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">老狼《模范情书》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我是你闲坐窗前的那颗橡树</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我是你初次流泪时手边的书</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我是你春夜注视着的那段蜡烛</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我是你秋天穿上的楚楚衣服</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我要你打开你挂在夏日的窗</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我要你牵我的手在午后徜徉</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我要你注视我注视你的目光</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">默默地告诉我初恋的忧伤</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">老狼《恋恋风尘》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那天黄昏开始飘起了白雪，忧伤开满山岗</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">等青春散场，午夜的电影写满古老的恋情</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">在黑暗中为年轻歌唱</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">蔡依林《柠檬草的味道》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">是不是回忆就是淡淡柠檬草，心酸里又有芳香的味道</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">五月天《如烟》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">七岁的那一年，抓住那只蝉</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">以为能抓住夏天</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">17岁的那年吻过他的脸</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">就以为和他能永远</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">张杰《仰望星空》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">这一天我开始仰望星空，发现星并不远</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">梦并不远，只要你踮起脚尖</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">许嵩《胡萝卜须》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">青春舞台来来往往，很多人人模狗样</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">偏见与傲慢轮番拜访方式不详</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">许嵩《北海道花季》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">七月北海道花儿日渐消瘦</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那时我向左，你却转身向右</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">林志炫《凤凰花开的路口》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">时光的河入海流终于我们分头走</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">没有哪个港口是永远的停留。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">朴树《那些花儿》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那片笑声让我想起我的那些花儿</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">在我生命的每个角落静静为我开着</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">如今这里荒草丛生没有了鲜花</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">好在曾经拥有你们的春秋和冬夏</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">杨宗纬《初爱》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">但你抛下课堂</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">翻过围墙只为了往一片大海</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">虽然你终究没等到我做你的骄傲</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">却永远是我生命中的美好</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">胡夏《那些年》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">桌垫下的老照片，无数回忆连结</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">今天男孩要赴女孩最后的约</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">又回到最初的起点，呆呆的站在镜子前</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">笨拙系上红色领带的结</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">将头发梳成大人模样，穿上一身帅气西装</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">等会儿见你一定比想象美</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">郁可唯《时间煮雨》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">风吹雨成花，时间追不上白马</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">老狼《情人劫》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那些照片早已烧成了灰烬</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">可能是回忆怎么点也点不着</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">马頔《时间里的》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那时你21岁了，为自由剪去你的长发</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">你不相信天是蓝的，装聋作哑</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br 