izing: border-box;\">我是你秋天穿上的楚楚衣服</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我要你打开你挂在夏日的窗</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我要你牵我的手在午后徜徉</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">我要你注视我注视你的目光</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">默默地告诉我初恋的忧伤</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">老狼《恋恋风尘》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那天黄昏开始飘起了白雪，忧伤开满山岗</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">等青春散场，午夜的电影写满古老的恋情</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">在黑暗中为年轻歌唱</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">蔡依林《柠檬草的味道》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">是不是回忆就是淡淡柠檬草，心酸里又有芳香的味道</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">五月天《如烟》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">七岁的那一年，抓住那只蝉</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">以为能抓住夏天</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">17岁的那年吻过他的脸</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">就以为和他能永远</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">张杰《仰望星空》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">这一天我开始仰望星空，发现星并不远</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">梦并不远，只要你踮起脚尖</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">许嵩《胡萝卜须》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">青春舞台来来往往，很多人人模狗样</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">偏见与傲慢轮番拜访方式不详</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">许嵩《北海道花季》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">七月北海道花儿日渐消瘦</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那时我向左，你却转身向右</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">林志炫《凤凰花开的路口》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">时光的河入海流终于我们分头走</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">没有哪个港口是永远的停留。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">朴树《那些花儿》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那片笑声让我想起我的那些花儿</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">在我生命的每个角落静静为我开着</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">如今这里荒草丛生没有了鲜花</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">好在曾经拥有你们的春秋和冬夏</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">杨宗纬《初爱》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">但你抛下课堂</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">翻过围墙只为了往一片大海</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">虽然你终究没等到我做你的骄傲</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">却永远是我生命中的美好</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">胡夏《那些年》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">桌垫下的老照片，无数回忆连结</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">今天男孩要赴女孩最后的约</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">又回到最初的起点，呆呆的站在镜子前</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">笨拙系上红色领带的结</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">将头发梳成大人模样，穿上一身帅气西装</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">等会儿见你一定比想象美</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">郁可唯《时间煮雨》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">风吹雨成花，时间追不上白马</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(45, 109, 75);box-sizing: border-box;\">老狼《情人劫》</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\">那些照片早已烧成了灰烬</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(142, 201, 101);box-sizing: border-box;\